HEADWORD: Wheelwright
<hw>Wheel"wright`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A man whose
occupation is to make or repair wheels and wheeled vehicles, as carts,
wagons, and the like.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

